Package com.promis.rtti.client

Interface Summary
Assignable Identifies object as possible target of assignment
Comparable Identifies object capable of comparing itself to other obejct
RttiClass Identifies class or interface type
RttiField Identifies public non-static field of a class.
RttiMethod Identifies class or interface method
 

Class Summary
Persistent Just a rename of RttiObject identifying an object capable of serialization, assigning and comparing.
Rtti Gives access to RTTI class parameters.
RttiConst Public constants uset by the RTTI library
RttiObject Base class for any objects which have RTTI info assigned to them.
 

Exception Summary
RttiIllegalArgumentException Thrown to indicate that a method has been passed an illegal or inappropriate argument.
RttiInvocationException Is thrown when exception is thrown inside RttiMethod.invoke
RttiReadOnlyException Is thrown when read-only field is attempt to be set.
UnableToAssignException Thrown when objects cannot be assigned
